arch book_read
name The great worm
msg
Legends of the past tell of a massive
worm-like monster. This worm could
tunnel underground at remarkable
speeds. Before this beast would
emerge,the ground would crackle with
electricity. When the great worm burst
forth from earth,a deafening roar
would reverbate throughout the
surrounding countryside. Lightning
bolts would flash from within its
yawning mouth. Sandstorms would arise
from around the worm's bulk. Its very
skin would glow with electricity.


endmsg
