arch tome
name the Elven Lands:three elf factions
msg
This continent has three Elven
kingdoms,the Green Elves,the Light
Elves,and the Dark elves.
The Light elves,their kingdom is
called the Elven Land of Yoer,are
continually at war with the Dark
elves,who live in the Elven Land of
Darkoth. The wood elves call their
kingdom,Flora's domain.
 The wood elves were once allies of
the light elves,until a terrible
tragity happened to the light elf
leader. He disapeared,and has not
been seen in these lands since.
 Certain groups speculate that the
Dwarves were responsible for King
Yoer's dissapearance. They think that
the Dwarves either killed him or
imprisoned him. 

endmsg
